        <dt class="- topic/dt " xtrc="dt:4;44:13" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/attributes/commonMapAttributes.dita">sequence </dt>
        <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrc="dd:4;45:13" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/attributes/commonMapAttributes.dita">Indicates that the order of the child topics is significant; output processors will
         typically link between them in order. </dd>
       </dlentry>
